2025>=0A=0A=0AProgramming note (1): Money Stuff is having a party! To celeb=
rate the 10th =0Aanniversary of the Money Stuff newsletter, Bloomberg Opini=
on is hosting a party =0Ain downtown New York on March 6. There will be foo=
d and drink and music and a =0Achat with me. Space is limited so pleaseRSVP=
 at this link <>.=0A=0AProgramming note (2): Money Stuff will be off the re=
st of the week, back on =0AMonday, Feb. 24. There is also no Money Stuff po=
dcast this week.=0A=0A=0APassive=0A=0AOne reason to buy stock in a company =
is that you think the company is good, =0Ayou like its management, and you =
